A Frog token is a reward from the frogs random event. These tokens can be exchanged for either a Prince outfit or Princess outfit (depending on gender), or a frog mask, by talking to Thessalia in Varrock, and selecting option "3. I have a frog token...". Thessalia will then prompt you with, "That entitles you to a free costume! Do you want a frog mask or a [prince/princess] outfit?"

Frog tokens cannot be withdrawn as notes and will not stack in your inventory when more than one is acquired.

Once the player has received the prince/princess outfit and Frog mask, the player can exchange tokens for additional copies of the outfit or mask.

A '''Frog token''' is a reward from the [[frogs]] [[random event]]. These tokens can be exchanged for either a [[Prince outfit]] or [[Princess outfit]] (depending on gender), or a [[frog mask]], by talking to [[Thessalia]] in [[Varrock]], and selecting option "3. I have a frog token...". Thessalia will then prompt you with, "That entitles you to a free costume! Do you want a frog mask or a [prince/princess] outfit?"

Frog tokens cannot be withdrawn as notes and will not stack in your inventory when more than one is acquired.

Once the player has received the [[Prince outfit|prince]]/[[princess outfit]] and [[Frog mask]], the player can exchange tokens for additional copies of the outfit or mask.
